name: qrcode-artistic-build
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "qrcode-artistic" %}
{% set version = "2.1.0" %}
{% set build_number = "0" %}
{% set min_python = ">=3.6" %}

package:
  name: {{ name }}-build
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  - folder: dist
    url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/qrcode-artistic-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: 29d43db365e32e5fab08afc7810e7890ece1a4d145b8a08364e1d9b4eaccf6ff
  - folder: src
    url: https://github.com/heuer/qrcode-artistic/archive/refs/tags/{{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: b83265d06a2b820fa8a7a9d8fa3ef94f727fecabd6df06af5797f052fd4eb2ab

build:
  number: {{ build_number }}
  noarch: python

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python {{ min_python }}
  run:
    - python {{ min_python }}

test:
  commands:
    - echo "tests in subpackages"

outputs:
  - name: {{ name }}-base
    version: {{ version }}
    build:
      build_number: {{ build_number }}
      noarch: python
      script: cd dist && {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
    requirements:
      host:
        - pip
        - python {{ min_python }}
      run:
        - pillow
        - python {{ min_python }}
        - segno >=1.0.2,<2
    test:
      requires:
        - pip
      imports:
        - qrcode_artistic
      commands:
        - pip check

  - name: {{ name }}-svg
    version: {{ version }}
    build:
      build_number: {{ build_number }}
      noarch: python
    requirements:
      host:
        - pip
        - python {{ min_python }}
      run:
        - python {{ min_python }}
        - {{ name }}-base =={{ version }}.*
        - cairosvg >=2.4,<3
    test:
      requires:
        - pip
      imports:
        - qrcode_artistic
      commands:
        - pip check

  - name: {{ name }}
    version: {{ version }}
    build:
      build_number: {{ build_number }}
      noarch: python
    requirements:
      host:
        - pip
        - python {{ min_python }}
      run:
        - python {{ min_python }}
        - {{ name }}-base =={{ version }}.*
        - {{ name }}-svg =={{ version }}.*
    test:
      source_files:
        - src/tests
        - src/images
      requires:
        - pip
        - pytest >=6,<7
        - pytest-cov
        - pyzbar >=0.1.8,<0.2  # [unix]
        # TODO: fix upstream https://github.com/conda-forge/pyzbar-feedstock/issues/1
        - zbar  # [unix]
      imports:
        - qrcode_artistic
      commands:
        - pip check
        - cd src
        - pytest -vv --cov=qrcode_artistic --cov-report=term-missing:skip-covered --cov-fail-under=100 --no-cov-on-fail  # [unix]

about:
  home: https://github.com/heuer/qrcode-artistic
  summary: Artistic (Micro) QR Code plugin for Segno
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file: dist/LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - bollwyvl
